cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with image captioning using natural language questions, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The agent's ability to continuously learn and expand its knowledge through interaction with humans involves machine learning (cs.AI) and reinforcement learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as the agent uses the teacher's expertise to improve its performance.
